headline: Winners And Losers Of Q4: Generac (NYSE:GNRC) Vs The Rest Of The Renewable Energy Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Generac (NYSE:GNRC) and the rest of the renewable energy stocks fared in Q4.
